props.text: I'm a passionate full-stack developer with 5+ years of experience in building web applications, APIs, and dynamic frontends. I love turning complex problems into simple, beautiful solutions.
Leading a team of 5 engineers in developing a scalable SaaS platform for enterprise task automation. Implemented CI/CD pipelines, improved performance by 40%, and mentored junior developers.
Developed web applications using React and Node.js for clients across healthcare and fintech industries. Designed REST APIs and integrated with third-party services.
An open-source Kanban-style project management tool built with React, Redux, and Firebase.
A dynamic portfolio and resume builder supporting export to PDF with customizable themes.
